        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value Proposition Section -->
  <section class="value-props">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Technology That Truly Cares</h2>
        <p>While others build chatbots, we've created AI companions that remember your mother's favorite stories, understand when your father needs encouragement, and know when to alert you that something's wrong.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="props-grid">
        <div class="prop-card">
          <div class="prop-icon">üíù</div>
          <h3>Genuine Connection</h3>
          <p>AI that remembers personal stories, celebrates small victories, and provides companionship that feels authentic and caring.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="prop-card">
          <div class="prop-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
          <h3>Peace of Mind</h3>
          <p>Gentle, continuous monitoring that catches warning signs early‚Äîpreventing crises before they happen, not just responding to them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="prop-card">
          <div class="prop-icon">üå±</div>
          <h3>Dignity Preserved</h3>
          <p>Respectful care that adapts to each person's needs without overwhelming them with constant questions or intrusive monitoring.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="prop-card">
          <div class="prop-icon">üë®‚Äçüë©‚Äçüëß‚Äçüë¶</div>
          <h3>Families United</h3>
          <p>Transparent updates that help families stay connected to their loved ones' daily lives, joys, and challenges.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Market Opportunity -->
  <section class="market-opportunity">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="market-content">
        <div class="market-text">
          <h2>Massive Market Opportunity</h2>
          <p class="market-subtitle">Senior mental health crisis meets AI breakthrough</p>
          
          <div class="market-stats">
            <div class="market-stat">
              <div class="market-number">$400B</div>
              <div class="market-label">Senior care industry</div>
            </div>
            <div class="market-stat">
              <div class="market-number">1.4M</div>
              <div class="market-label">Seniors in assisted living (US)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="market-stat">
              <div class="market-number">$15M+</div>
              <div class="market-label">3-year ARR potential</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="market-highlights">
            <div class="highlight">‚úì Post-COVID mental health crisis in senior care</div>
            <div class="highlight">‚úì CMS pushing value-based care outcomes</div>
